---
title: Herby Crumbed Beef Schnitzels with Slaw, Veggie Fries & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Who doesn’t love a good, crumbed schnitzel? We've switched the protein up by using beef, then paired it with a crunchy radish slaw
and oven-roasted veggie fries. For a herby finishing touch, we've added dill and parsley mayo to make this a certified household hit.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/herby-crumbed-beef-schnitzels-24f4d6fc.jpg
